        <actionDate>2020-03-12</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2020-05-28T15:09:00Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Food Allergy Safety, Treatment, Education, and Research Act of 2020 or the FASTER Act of 2020</b></p> <p>This bill expands&nbsp;the definition of<i> major food allergen</i> for purposes of certain food-labeling requirements&nbsp;to specifically include sesame. In addition, the Department of Health and Human Services must report on certain information related to food allergy research and data collection activities. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
